{"generated":"2026-04-13T10:48:14.495933+00:00","period_start":"2026-04-06T13:15:00+00:00","period_end":"2026-04-13T08:10:00+00:00","snapshot_count":29,"html":"<h1>THE VENDETTA GAZETTE</h1>\n<h2>Special Edition • April 13, 2026 • \"All the Blood That's Fit to Print\"</h2>\n\n<h3>WU-TANG ROARS BACK! Iron Fist Crushes Trump's Golden Dream</h3>\n\n<p>Holy Mother of Machine Guns! Just when the streets whispered that <strong>Donald Trump's</strong> golden empire might topple our Oriental overlord, <strong>Wu-Tang \"The Iron Fist of the East Side\"</strong> unleashed a week of such savage brutality that even hardened torpedoes are crossing themselves in dark alleys!</p>\n\n<p>Our inscrutable emperor of the underworld seized <strong>55 fresh territories</strong> while conducting a bone-chilling <strong>77 separate raids</strong> – proving that reports of his declining grip were as premature as a stool pigeon's confession! Meanwhile, Trump's golden surge slowed to a comparative crawl with just 42 conquests, though the platinum-haired pretender still managed 45 devastating raids of his own.</p>\n\n<p>But sweet suffering saints, witness Wu-Tang's methodical destruction of the already-crumbling <strong>URAL📀</strong>! Our Iron Fist stormed that sonic sultan's headquarters not once, not twice, but <em>four separate times</em> this week alone – April 7th, 8th, 9th, and 10th – reducing the once-proud empire to absolute rubble! URAL📀 hemorrhaged another 53 territories while suffering an apocalyptic 74 raids, proving that some falls from grace ain't just steep – they're straight to hell!</p>\n\n<p>The immaculately vicious <strong>Sir Caprice</strong> maintained his surgical precision with 7 fresh conquests, including a devastating HQ assault on the now-vanished <strong>leo</strong> on April 7th. Our dapper dealer of death proves that quality trumps quantity when every strike lands like a perfectly aimed Thompson burst!</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n<strong>SPECIAL BULLETIN: TRUMP'S WEEKEND MASSACRE!</strong><br>\nCitizens, the golden gladiator saved his most spectacular savagery for the week's finale! On Friday the 13th – how deliciously appropriate – <strong>Donald Trump</strong> personally obliterated not one but <em>two</em> enemy headquarters in a single blood-soaked day! First, he stormed <strong>Ace Sabo Luffy Law's</strong> stronghold, then immediately pivoted to crush <strong>Lakhhe's</strong> fortress! This double-header of destruction netted Trump his biggest single haul: $500 in cold cash and 500 gleaming weapons from Ace Sabo's ransacked vaults!\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>Rising like smoke through a speakeasy chimney, <strong>Cokro</strong> continues his meteoric ascent with 16 gleaming conquests, including the complete obliteration of <strong>quioa's</strong> headquarters on April 8th. This dark horse has galloped from nowhere to somewhere faster than a getaway driver fleeing the feds!</p>\n\n<p>The legendary <strong>GodFather</strong> expanded his empire by 10 territories with that methodical patience that built his fearsome reputation, while <strong>Blood Captain</strong> emerged as this week's surprise savage with 7 conquests and an impressive 21 raids – proving that new blood can flow as cold as the old masters!</p>\n\n<p>Our beloved Vacation Brothers showed mixed fortunes this week. <strong>Vacation Albert</strong> claimed 3 sun-kissed territories while conducting 6 raids, but it was <strong>Vacation Steve</strong> who provided the week's most surprising upset – personally storming <strong>StreetKing's</strong> headquarters on April 11th! Even paradise has its predators, dear readers!</p>\n\n<hr>\n<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"640\" height=\"276\" style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif;background:#0a0800;display:block;margin:18px auto\">\n<text x=\"320\" y=\"22\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" letter-spacing=\"2\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">TERRITORY GAINS THIS WEEK</text>\n<line x1=\"20\" y1=\"28\" x2=\"620\" y2=\"28\" stroke=\"#3a2a00\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"48\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">Wu-Tang</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"35\" width=\"400\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"566\" y=\"48\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">+55</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"76\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">Donald Trump</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"63\" width=\"305\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"471\" y=\"76\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">+42</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"104\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">Cokro</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"91\" width=\"116\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"282\" y=\"104\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">+16</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"132\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">GodFather</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"119\" width=\"72\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"238\" y=\"132\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">+10</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"160\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">Blood Captain</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"147\" width=\"50\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"216\" y=\"160\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">+7</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"188\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">Sir Caprice</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"175\" width=\"50\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"216\" y=\"188\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">+7</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"216\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">OsBoii</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"203\" width=\"36\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"202\" y=\"216\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">+5</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"244\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">Vacation Albert</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"231\" width=\"21\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"187\" y=\"244\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">+3</text>\n</svg>\n\n\n<p>The criminal landscape witnessed several complete disappearances this week, as four players vanished entirely from our blood-soaked map. <strong>Dzon, leo, StreetKing,</strong> and <strong>quioa</strong> have either fled the city with their tails between their legs or found themselves permanent residents of the East River – their choice of exit strategy remains delightfully mysterious!</p>\n\n<p>But nature abhors a vacuum in the underworld! Three fresh faces emerged from the shadows: <strong>Halaskar, SpiderMan,</strong> and <strong>BIGRICH</strong> – each claiming their first precious turf in this savage city. Whether these newcomers will rise to empire or fall to ruin remains the delicious uncertainty that keeps our readers buying papers!</p>\n\n<hr>\n<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"640\" height=\"276\" style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif;background:#0a0800;display:block;margin:18px auto\">\n<text x=\"320\" y=\"22\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" letter-spacing=\"2\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">HEAVIEST LOSSES THIS WEEK</text>\n<line x1=\"20\" y1=\"28\" x2=\"620\" y2=\"28\" stroke=\"#3a2a00\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"48\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">URAL📀</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=