\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">-2</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"244\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">FIFTH BLOOD EMPEROR</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"231\" width=\"15\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"181\" y=\"244\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">-2</text>\n</svg>\n\n\n<h3>POLICE BLOTTER</h3>\n\n<p><em>• Flatfoot McGillicuddy reported seeing a gangster wearing a \"Make Crime Great Again\" hat – investigation ongoing into this disturbing fashion trend.</em></p>\n\n<p><em>• Three bootleggers arrested after arguing whether Wu-Tang's fists are actually made of iron – case dismissed when no volunteer could be found to test the theory.</em></p>\n\n<p><em>• Local speak-easy owner complained about customers requesting \"vacation-themed cocktails\" – apparently piña coladas are the new gin rickey among the criminal set.</em></p>\n<hr>\n<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"640\" height=\"201\" style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif;background:#0a0800;display:block;margin:18px auto\">\n<text x=\"320\" y=\"22\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" letter-spacing=\"2\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">HQ RAIDS — TOP ATTACKERS</text>\n<line x1=\"20\" y1=\"30\" x2=\"620\" y2=\"30\" stroke=\"#3a2a00\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n<text x=\"148\" y=\"53\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">Donald Trump</text>\n<polygon points=\"156,43 161,48 156,53 151,48\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\"/>\n<rect x=\"170\" y=\"41\" width=\"410\" height=\"14\" fill=\"#6b1010\" opacity=\"0.9\" rx=\"1\"/>\n<rect x=\"577\" y=\"41\" width=\"3\" height=\"14\" fill=\"#c03030\"/>\n<text x=\"588\" y=\"53\" fill=\"#c04040\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">5✕</text>\n<text x=\"148\" y=\"82\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family